---
title: Quick Crumbed Fish & Chips with Garden Salad & Garlic Aioli
description: It’s a classic, it’s a favourite for all, it’s the answer to your cravings, a steaming plate of fish and chips. That’s right we’re trying our hand at this superstar dish, bringing it to your kitchen with a seasoned crumb for the fish fillets, a must-have side of chips, fresh salad and of course some aioli. You won’t be needing that takeaway menu anymore.
